query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS assessmentQuestions (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  assessmentId INT NOT NULL,
  catalogReferenceId VARCHAR(50),
  questionId VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  dimensionCode ENUM('process','people','technology','data','governance') NOT NULL,
  dimensionLabel VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  questionText TEXT NOT NULL,
  answerScale JSON NOT NULL,
  weight DECIMAL(3,2) NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX assessment_questions_assessment_idx (assessmentId),
  INDEX assessment_questions_dimension_idx (assessmentId, dimensionCode),
  FOREIGN KEY (assessmentId) REFERENCES capabilityAssessments(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
)
